                 <li><strong><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coherent_optical_communication" target="_blank" class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-cyan-400 underline decoration-dotted hover:text-indigo-500 dark:hover:text-cyan-300">Coherent Transceivers</a>:</strong> High-speed optical processing.</li>
                 <li><strong><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erbium-doped_fiber_amplifier" target="_blank" class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-cyan-400 underline decoration-dotted hover:text-indigo-500 dark:hover:text-cyan-300">EDFAs</a>:</strong> Optical signal amplification.</li>
